HEADWORD: Retiarius
<hw>Re`ti*a"ri*us</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
<ets>rete</ets> a net.]</ety> <fld>(Rom.Antiq.)</fld> <def>A gladiator
